{
  "stem": "13471.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Well, that's-- that's-- that's a man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That's a human being.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was hung.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had him dead to rights.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Hitler had-- had ordered that all of the Canadian [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] raiders-- what do they call them, that raided the coast of Dieppe, that were captured were to be executed.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In spite of the fact-- after they were captured.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he-- I can't think of his name-- transmitted that order over his own signature.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, this general.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Which in itself is documentary prima facie evidence of his co-guilt.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was hung.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Streicher was the-- remember-- was the one that edited and published this Jew-baiting journal called [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- the Stormtrooper.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Storm Attack, or the Attack Stormer, Stormtrooper, all right.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he-- he put the most hideous things in there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Lies, all of them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Every-- you could look at a new edition of this, and there would be a big thing, and then always down in the right-hand corner, a Jew would back a innocent, virginal, white, German girl into a corner and rape her.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] put your hand right there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There it is, that story, with a new, different name and a different-- the Germans wouldn't have anything to do with him.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, he was just another one of these animals.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was-- he was executed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Speer was given a-- I think it was a 15-year life-- a 15-year sentence.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Served it and was later released.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Executed.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was-- he was condemned to be hanged, but he-- he sweet-talked, apparently-- well, nobody's quite sure-- a Texas captain, who was one of the guards, into telling him or indicating to him, to Goering, in advance, when the execution was to take place.",
      "word_count": 44
    }
  ],
